you can do also.

511
00:45:12,444 --> 00:45:16,379
<i>The power of God
is within you!</i>

512
00:45:16,381 --> 00:45:19,716
All that is required
is that you believe.

513
00:45:22,387 --> 00:45:25,455
Let us pray.

514
00:45:25,457 --> 00:45:28,958
<i>Lord, we welcome You
amongst us this morning.</i>

515
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:32,295
