My sense is he's taken quite
a shine to me being here.

540
00:47:28,012 --> 00:47:29,545
You're mistaken.

541
00:47:29,547 --> 00:47:31,581
It's that pretty
bean-eating wife of yours...

542
00:47:31,583 --> 00:47:33,482
( gunshot )

543
