545
00:47:57,008 --> 00:47:59,375
( groaning )

546
00:48:07,051 --> 00:48:09,118
Get him out of here.

547
00:48:09,120 --> 00:48:11,554
( muttering )

548
00:48:13,291 --> 00:48:15,024
Get off!

549
00:48:15,026 --> 00:48:18,027
Not bad for the son
