568
00:49:43,114 --> 00:49:44,513
- He wouldn't do that...
- Damn it, Marisol!

569
00:49:44,515 --> 00:49:46,415
I saw it myself!

570
00:49:49,087 --> 00:49:51,487
Why are you speaking
