571
00:49:54,659 --> 00:49:56,325
All right.
Hey.

572
00:49:56,327 --> 00:49:59,128
Hey, it's all right,
it's all right.

573
00:49:59,130 --> 00:50:00,329
It's all right.

574
00:50:03,167 --> 00:50:07,236
<i>- ( piano music playing )</i>
