712
01:01:47,404 --> 01:01:49,337
It's okay, it's okay.
I'm here.

713
01:01:49,339 --> 01:01:51,039
Calm down, calm down.

714
01:01:51,041 --> 01:01:53,942
I'm here.
I'm here.

