<i>( man coughs )</i>

723
01:03:38,949 --> 01:03:41,016
Gentlemen...

724
01:03:41,018 --> 01:03:43,118
pick your prey.

725
01:04:07,144 --> 01:04:09,444
That one.

726
01:04:09,446 --> 01:04:11,012
The woman?

727
01:04:11,014 --> 01:04:13,014
You are twisted,
