749
01:08:33,343 --> 01:08:35,243
Abraham:
<i>Good job, son.</i>

750
01:08:45,822 --> 01:08:48,756
You gotta take
the scalp, George.

751
01:08:48,758 --> 01:08:51,626
<i>Nothing to it...
quick slit and a pull.</i>

752
01:08:54,531 --> 01:08:57,465
Isaac: <i>I guarantee you,
she'd take yours.</i>

753
01:08:57,467 --> 01:08:59,868
They're as wild
